title: Princess Nirvana
overview: When Changning Princess Chu Ziqian woke up, she turned into Lin Yan, the daughter of Lin Shangshu, sitting on the wedding sedan to marry the seventh prince Zhao Qing. Everyone thought that the Seventh Prince and Princess Changning were childhood sweethearts, but Chu Ziqian actually claimed that the Seventh Prince not only refused to marry and humiliated her, but also poisoned her. God has given this opportunity, and Chu Ziqian will definitely use Lin Yan's identity to take revenge.
